summary: Completed comprehensive testing of SheHuMaan Orchestrator MVP - AI-powered work-life balance platform for women in IT. Backend API with OpenAI GPT-5.2 integration working correctly, frontend questionnaire flow and dashboard functioning well.

flaky_endpoints.issue: AI generation takes 30-60 seconds causing potential timeouts
flaky_endpoints.impact: Users may think the app is broken if no loading indicator
flaky_endpoints.workaround: Loading indicator already implemented in frontend

ui_bugs.issue: Clipboard write permission denied error overlay appears
ui_bugs.details: Browser security feature blocking clipboard access - functionality works but shows error overlay

passed_tests: Landing page loads with proper branding and CTA buttons
Questionnaire 4-step form with all input fields working
AI-powered empathy explanation generation using OpenAI GPT-5.2
AI-powered workplace suggestions and email drafts
Simulated prediction system for stress/burnout scores working
Dashboard displays stress meters, burnout meters, key stressors
Dashboard shows 7-day plan with accordion functionality
Dashboard shows safety tips and India-specific resources
Navigation flow: Landing → Questionnaire → Dashboard → Back to Landing
action_item_for_main_agent: Minor clipboard permission issue on dashboard copy functionality - consider adding fallback text selection or user instruction tooltip. Overall application is production-ready.
